name: symphonie de lumières
description:
Star clusters forming into galaxies, vast and beautiful.

This 1920x1080 HD video was created from images captured by the nasa/esa hubble telescope, stitched together, before seamless transitions were created to bring out some fantastical colours and shapes that have to seen to be believed.

“Do not feel lonely, the entire universe is inside of you.” 
– Rumi

I love this piece and it is my pleasure to share it with you.

I give you symphonie de lumières

Music credit to Ogg Music for bringing the whole piece together
